# Windsurf Configuration

## Formatting Rules
- ALWAYS use prettier for all files
- Format on save MUST be enabled
- Jenkinsfile MUST use groovy parser with 2 space indentation
- NO tabs - only spaces
- Consistent 2-space indentation for Jenkins Pipeline

## File Associations
- Jenkinsfile -> groovy language
- Use prettier-plugin-groovy for Jenkinsfile formatting

## Editor Settings
- tabWidth: 2
- useTabs: false
- editor.formatOnSave: true
- editor.defaultFormatter: prettier

## Jenkins Pipeline Specific
- Use 2 spaces for each indentation level
- Align stage blocks consistently
- Format sh scripts with proper indentation
